title: Washington State Department of Transportation, National Forests, Washington, 1996
name: Washington State Department of Transportation, National Forests, Washington, 1996
description:
Abstract:

      United States Department of Agriculture Forest Service lands are shown as polygons in this data set. Each named forest is a discrete set of areas.

Purpose: This data set is used as a reference layer at the Washington State Department of Transportation to depict National Forests at a small scale.

author.source: GIS Implementation Team, Washington State Department of Transportation
